(337,'*\'\'\'Here the example of Master-Master MySQL replication between Server-X and Server-Y\'\'\'\n*<u>Install MySQL-Server and dependencies in both servers</u>\n<pre>yum install -y mysql-community-server-8.0.27-1.el7.x86_64.rpm mysql-community-client-8.0.27-1.el7.x86_64.rpm</pre>\n\n*<u>Configure my.cnf in both servers with minimal requirement of replication</u>\n*\'\'\'Server-X\'\'\'\n<pre>\n    server-id=1\n    log-bin=\"mysql-bin\"\n    binlog-do-db=name_of_database\n    replicate-do-db=name_of_database\n    relay-log=\"mysql-relay-log\"\n    auto-increment-offset = 1\n</pre>\n*\'\'\'Server-Y\'\'\'\n<pre>\n    server-id=2\n    log-bin=\"mysql-bin\"\n    binlog-do-db=name_of_database\n    replicate-do-db=name_of_database\n    relay-log=\"mysql-relay-log\"\n    auto-increment-offset = 2\n</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Restart MySQL in both servers\'\'\'\n<pre>systemctl restart mysqld && systemctl enable mysqld</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Create Replicate user in both servers\'\'\'\n<pre>\nmysql> CREATE USER \'replicate\'@\'%\' IDENTIFIED BY \'change_me\';\nmysql> GRANT REPLICATION SLAVE ON *.* TO \'replicate\'@\'%\';\n</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Now take a backup of Server-X\'\'\'\n<pre>mysqldump -uroot -p name_of_database > name_of_database.sql</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Restore the database in Server-Y\'\'\'\n<pre>mysql -uroot -p name_of_database < name_of_database.sql</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Check master status in Server-X\'\'\'\n<pre>\nmysql> SHOW MASTER STATUS;\n+------------------+----------+------------------+------------------+\n| File             | Position | Binlog_Do_DB     | Binlog_Ignore_DB |\n+------------------+----------+------------------+------------------+\n| mysql-bin.000001 | 154      | name_of_database |                  |\n+------------------+----------+------------------+------------------+\n1 row in set (0.00 sec)\n</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Now in Server-Y\'\'\'\n<pre>\nmysql> CHANGE MASTER TO MASTER_HOST=\'<IP_Of_Server-X>\', MASTER_USER=\'replicate\', MASTER_PASSWORD=\'changeMe\', MASTER_LOG_FILE=\'mysql-bin.000001\', MASTER_LOG_POS=154;\nmysql> START SLAVE;\n\nCheck the master status\nmysql> SHOW MASTER STATUS;\n+------------------+----------+------------------+------------------+\n| File             | Position | Binlog_Do_DB     | Binlog_Ignore_DB |\n+------------------+----------+------------------+------------------+\n| mysql-bin.000001 | 146      | name_of_database |                  |\n+------------------+----------+------------------+------------------+\n1 row in set (0.00 sec) </pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Now in Server-X\'\'\'\n<pre>\nmysql> CHANGE MASTER TO MASTER_HOST=\'<IP_Of_Server-Y>\', MASTER_USER=\'replicate\', MASTER_PASSWORD=\'changeMe\', MASTER_LOG_FILE=\'mysql-bin.000001\', MASTER_LOG_POS=146;\nmysql> START SLAVE;</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'All completed, now check the replication status in both servers\'\'\'\n<pre>mysql> SHOW SLAVE STATUS \\G;\n\n*************************** 1. row ***************************\n               Slave_IO_State: Waiting for source to send event\n                  Master_Host: <IP_Of_Server-X>\n                  Master_User: repl\n                  Master_Port: 3306\n                Connect_Retry: 60\n              Master_Log_File: mysql-bin.000001\n          Read_Master_Log_Pos: 91443\n               Relay_Log_File: mysql-relay-log.000002\n                Relay_Log_Pos: 33895\n        Relay_Master_Log_File: mysql-bin.000001\n             Slave_IO_Running: Yes\n            Slave_SQL_Running: Yes\n              Replicate_Do_DB: name_of_database\n          Replicate_Ignore_DB:\n           Replicate_Do_Table:\n       Replicate_Ignore_Table:\n      Replicate_Wild_Do_Table:\n  Replicate_Wild_Ignore_Table:\n                   Last_Errno: 0\n                   Last_Error:\n                 Skip_Counter: 0\n          Exec_Master_Log_Pos: 91443\n              Relay_Log_Space: 34104\n              Until_Condition: None\n               Until_Log_File:\n                Until_Log_Pos: 0\n           Master_SSL_Allowed: No\n           Master_SSL_CA_File:\n           Master_SSL_CA_Path:\n              Master_SSL_Cert:\n            Master_SSL_Cipher:\n               Master_SSL_Key:\n        Seconds_Behind_Master: 0\nMaster_SSL_Verify_Server_Cert: No\n                Last_IO_Errno: 0\n                Last_IO_Error:\n               Last_SQL_Errno: 0\n               Last_SQL_Error:\n  Replicate_Ignore_Server_Ids:\n             Master_Server_Id: 1\n                  Master_UUID: 4485ec9d-319f-11ec-91b0-0050568c0122\n             Master_Info_File: mysql.slave_master_info\n                    SQL_Delay: 0\n          SQL_Remaining_Delay: NULL\n      Slave_SQL_Running_State: Replica has read all relay log; waiting for more updates\n           Master_Retry_Count: 86400\n                  Master_Bind:\n      Last_IO_Error_Timestamp:\n     Last_SQL_Error_Timestamp:\n               Master_SSL_Crl:\n           Master_SSL_Crlpath:\n           Retrieved_Gtid_Set:\n            Executed_Gtid_Set:\n                Auto_Position: 0\n         Replicate_Rewrite_DB:\n                 Channel_Name:\n           Master_TLS_Version:\n       Master_public_key_path:\n        Get_master_public_key: 0\n            Network_Namespace:\n1 row in set, 1 warning (0.01 sec)\n</pre>','utf-8'),
