(674,'*\'\'\'SMTP Relay Details for RIL\'\'\'\n<pre>\nOLD:emailsmtp.ril.com, port 25, Access:Anonymous\nNew:LB IP:10.129.79.220\nEmail Server IP:10.129.78.138, 10.129.78.139\nPort: 25\nAccess:Anonymous\n</pre>\n*\'\'\'Remove all iptables rules\'\'\'\n<pre>iptables -P INPUT ACCEPT && iptables -P FORWARD ACCEPT && iptables -P OUTPUT ACCEPT && iptables -t nat -F && iptables -t mangle -F && iptables -F && iptables -X && iptables-save </pre>\n*\'\'\'SSL Issue in Git command\'\'\'\n<pre>git -c http.sslVerify=false (options)\ngit config --global http.sslVerify = false</pre>\n*\'\'\'DMZ Port opening for Kubernetes Cluster\'\'\'\n<pre>\nSource: Kubernetes all Non-DMZ Nodes\nDestination: All DMZ nodes\nPorts: 22/TCP,6443/TCP,2379-2380/TCP,10245-10260/TCP, 6780-6790/TCP, <NodePort_IP>/TCP (Bi-directional)\nDuration: Permanent</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'[[Check iptables in Kubernetes]]\n\n\n*\'\'\'Remove-Bridge-Network\'\'\'\n<pre>Install bridge-utils\nbrctl show | ip link set virbr0 down | brctl delbr virbr0\n</pre>\n*\'\'\'Docker-compose\'\'\'\n<pre>curl -L \"https://github.com/docker/compose/releases/download/1.23.2/docker-compose-$(uname -s)-$(uname -m)\" -o /usr/bin/docker-compose && chmod 755 /usr/bin/docker-compose</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Create a CSR for single domain\'\'\'\n<pre>openssl req -new -newkey rsa:2048 -nodes -keyout domain.key -out domain.csr </pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Create CSR from config flie \'\'\'(<i>Multiple Domains</i>)\n<pre>openssl req -new -out domain.csr -newkey rsa:2048 -nodes -sha256 -keyout domain.key -config domain.conf</pre>\n<pre>Sample Config File\n[req]\ndistinguished_name = Domain_certs\nreq_extensions = v3_req\ndefault_keyfile = domain.key\nprompt = no\n\n[Domain_certs]\nC = IN\nST = Maharastra\nL = Mumbai\nO = RIL\nOU = Retail IT\nCN = domain.ril.com\n\n[v3_req]\nkeyUsage = keyEncipherment, dataEncipherment\nextendedKeyUsage = serverAuth\nsubjectAltName = @alt_names\n\n[alt_names]\nDNS.1 = domain.ril.com\nDNS.2 = domain1.ril.com\nDNS.3 = domain2.ril.com\nDNS.4 = domain3.ril.com </pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Create PFX file from certificate files\'\'\'\n* PFX File format is required for WAF and LB configuration\n<pre>\nopenssl pkcs12 -export -in domain.crt -inkey domain.key -out domain.pfx -certfile domain_bundle.crt\n\nProvide Password:\n</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'MediaWiki Side Bar Edit\'\'\'\n<pre>Open\nhttps://wiki.rril.ril.com/index.php/MediaWiki:Sidebar </pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Kubernetes Secrets\'\'\'\n<pre>\ndev:			  \nkubectl -n kube-rrip create secret generic rdip-secret --from-literal=sap.spring.user=RRIPSAP --from-literal=sap.spring.pass=DI4frtZQyEc8VTXCCPxbdkcgKe6OqJMT --from-literal=db.spring.url=jdbc:oracle:thin:@10.21.54.22:1521:TIBDEV --from-literal=db.spring.user=tibco --from-literal=db.spring.pass=\"ENC(OG7nPpz8c4R+HCHpfJtGjQ==)\" --from-literal=kafka.spring.brokers=rripdevmaster1.ril.com:9092,rripdevmaster2.ril.com:9092,rripdevmaster3.ril.com:9092\n\nQA:\nkubectl -n kube-rrip create secret generic rdip-secret --from-literal=sap.spring.user=RRIPSAP --from-literal=sap.spring.pass=DI4frtZQyEc8VTXCCPxbdkcgKe6OqJMT --from-literal=db.spring.url=jdbc:oracle:thin:@10.129.34.194:1521:TIBSIT --from-literal=db.spring.user=tibco --from-literal=db.spring.pass=\"ENC(qkMeV7F21dYHVykJYc/FlPZ0kPqrcP7K)\" --from-literal=kafka.spring.brokers=rripqamaster1.ril.com:9092,rripqamaster2.ril.com:9092,rripqamaster3.ril.com:9092\n\nPreProd:\nkubectl -n kube-rrip create secret generic rdip-secret --from-literal=sap.spring.user=RRIPSAP --from-literal=sap.spring.pass=PEZ3FLtQPlxTTJJsQicv9Q0tZr0hO+2Z --from-literal=db.spring.url=jdbc:oracle:thin:@10.131.162.135:1521:RRTIB01 --from-literal=db.spring.user=tibco --from-literal=db.spring.pass=\"ENC(BGuzeT4B1CfVV93Z1lCdwkeYNiqxMTZ2)\" --from-literal=kafka.spring.brokers=rrippreprodmaster1.ril.com:9092,rrippreprodmaster2.ril.com:9092,rrippreprodmaster3.ril.com:9092\n\nProd:\nkubectl -n kube-rrip-dmz create secret generic rdip-secret --from-literal=sap.spring.user=RRIPSAP --from-literal=db.spring.url=jdbc:oracle:thin:@10.12