(728,'* \'\'\'<u>This is the guide for NVIDIA driver and runtime installation in RHEL/CentOS</u>\'\'\'\n\n*\'\'\'Prerequisites\'\'\'\n* Verify the GPU device\n<pre>lspci | grep -i nvidia</pre>\n*Update the system\n<pre>yum update -y\nyum install tar bzip2 make automake gcc gcc-c++ pciutils elfutils-libelf-devel libglvnd-devel -y\nyum install https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm -y</pre>\n*Configure NVIDIA repository\n<pre>distribution=rhel7\nARCH=$( /bin/arch )\nyum-config-manager --add-repo http://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/repos/$distribution/${ARCH}/cuda-$distribution.repo</pre>\n*For CentOS 7, ensure that the system has the correct Linux kernel sources from the CentOS repositories:\n<pre>yum install -y kernel-devel-$(uname -r) kernel-headers-$(uname -r)\nyum clean expire-cache</pre>\n*Install latest NVIDIA Drivers\n<pre>yum install nvidia-driver-latest-dkms cuda cuda-driver -y</pre>\n*Configure Repository for container runtime\n<pre>curl -s -L https://nvidia.github.io/nvidia-docker/$distribution/nvidia-docker.repo | sudo tee /etc/yum.repos.d/nvidia-docker.repo</pre>\n*Install container runtime (Required Docker)\n<pre>yum install nvidia-container-toolkit nvidia-container-runtime nvidia-container-toolkit-base -y</pre>\n*Configure Docker for default NVIDIA runtime\n<pre>\ncat > /etc/docker/daemon.json << EOF\n{\n  \"exec-opts\": [\"native.cgroupdriver=systemd\"],\n  \"log-driver\": \"json-file\",\n  \"log-opts\": {\n    \"max-size\": \"100m\"\n  },\n   \"default-runtime\": \"nvidia\",\n   \"runtimes\": {\n      \"nvidia\": {\n            \"path\": \"/usr/bin/nvidia-container-runtime\",\n            \"runtimeArgs\": []\n      }\n   }\n}\nEOF</pre>\n<pre>systemctl daemon-reload && systemctl restart docker</pre>\n*Check container runtime\n<pre>docker info|grep nvidia\n*Check NVIDIA system driver\n<pre>cat /proc/driver/nvidia/version</pre>\n\n*Update library path for NVIDIA\n<pre>echo \"export PATH=/usr/local/cuda/bin:$PATH\" >> /etc/bashrc\necho \"export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/local/cuda/lib64:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH\" >> /etc/bashrc</pre>\n\n*Now \'\'\'REBOOT\'\'\' the system\n\n*After reboot check NVIDIA System driver\n<pre>nvidia-smi</pre>\n\n*Check NVIDIA runtime with Docker\n<pre>docker run --gpus all docker.rril.ril.com/cuda:10.0-base nvidia-smi</pre>\n<pre>OUTPUT should be:\n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| NVIDIA-SMI 525.60.13    Driver Version: 525.60.13    CUDA Version: 12.0     |\n|-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n| GPU  Name        Persistence-M| Bus-Id        Disp.A | Volatile Uncorr. ECC |\n| Fan  Temp  Perf  Pwr:Usage/Cap|         Memory-Usage | GPU-Util  Compute M. |\n|                               |                      |               MIG M. |\n|===============================+======================+======================|\n|   0  Tesla T4            Off  | 00000000:00:04.0 Off |                    0 |\n| N/A   65C    P0    31W /  70W |      0MiB / 15360MiB |      0%      Default |\n|                               |                      |                  N/A |\n+-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n|   1  Tesla T4            Off  | 00000000:00:05.0 Off |                    0 |\n| N/A   77C    P0    36W /  70W |      0MiB / 15360MiB |      0%      Default |\n|                               |                      |                  N/A |\n+-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n|   2  Tesla T4            Off  | 00000000:00:06.0 Off |                    0 |\n| N/A   68C    P0    30W /  70W |      0MiB / 15360MiB |      0%      Default |\n|                               |                      |                  N/A |\n+-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n|   3  Tesla T4            Off  | 00000000:00:07.0 Off |                    0 |\n| N/A   68C    P0    29W /  70W |      0MiB / 15360MiB |      0%      Default |\n|                               |                      |                  N/A |\n+-------------------------------+----------------------+----------------------+\n\n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n| Processes:                                                                  |\n|  GPU   GI   CI        PID   Type   Process name                  GPU Memory |\n|        ID   ID                                                   Usage      |\n|=============================================================================|\n|  No running processes found                                                 |\n+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+\n</pre>','utf-8'),
