(733,'* \'\'\'Prepare backup location\'\'\'\n<pre>\nDo followings in all elasticsearch nodes\n\nmkdir -p /data/elastic/backup\nchown -R elasticsearch:elasticsearch /data/elastic/backup\n\necho \'path.repo: [\"/data/elastic/backup\"]\' >> /etc/elasticsearch/elasticsearch.yml\n\nsystemctl restart elasticsearch </pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Prepare a snapshot repository\'\'\'\n<pre>\ncurl -m 30 -u elastic:xxxxxxxxxxxx -XPUT http://localhost:9200/_snapshot/rituraj_backup -H \'Content-Type: application/json\' -d \'{\n \"type\": \"fs\",\n \"settings\": {\n   \"location\": \"/data/elastic/backup\",\n   \"compress\": true\n }\n}\'</pre>\n<pre>Successful output\n{\"acknowledged\" : true}</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Get information about snapshot repository\'\'\'\n<pre>curl -u elastic:xxxxxxxxxxxx -XGET http://localhost:9200/_snapshot/rituraj_backup?pretty\n\nSample output:\n{\n  \"rituraj_backup\" : {\n    \"type\" : \"fs\",\n    \"settings\" : {\n      \"location\" : \"/data/elastic/backup\"\n    }\n  }\n}</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Create backup of all indices\'\'\'\n<pre>\ncurl -u elastic:xxxxxxxxxxxx -XPUT http://localhost:9200/_snapshot/rituraj_backup/backup-<date>?pretty\n</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Create backup for a index\'\'\'\n<pre>curl -u elastic:xxxxxxxxxxxx -XPUT http://localhost:9200/_snapshot/rituraj_backup/filebeat-<date>?wait_for_completion=true -H \'Content-Type: application/json\' -d \'{\n \"indices\": \"filebeat-7.12.0-2021.04.19-000001\",\n \"ignore_unavailable\": true,\n \"include_global_state\": false\n}\'<pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Check the backup\'\'\'\n<pre>curl -u elastic:xxxxxxxxxxxx -XPUT http://localhost:9200/_snapshot/rituraj_backup/filebeat-<date>?pretty</pre>\n\n*\'\'\'Restore the backup\'\'\'\n<pre>curl -u elastic:xxxxxxxxxxxx -XPUT http://localhost:9200/_snapshot/rituraj_backup/filebeat-<date>/_restore?pretty</pre>\n<pre>If success, get following message:\n{\n  \"accepted\" : true\n}</pre>','utf-8'),
